entry.title: Shooting at Jerusalem Synagogue Kills Seven People
entry.content: Israeli authorities say the assailant was fatally shot after what they called a terrorist attack.

entry.title: Russia Seeks Gains in Ukraine Before Western Tanks Turn Up
entry.content: Moscow’s forces pressed an eastern offensive, trying to seize an advantage in the months before tanks pledged by Kyiv’s allies begin to arrive on the battlefield.

entry.title: Alps Ski Resorts Brace for a Future With Less Snow
entry.content: With snow scarce, some resorts promote biking trails and adventure parks, others try to move their ski runs to higher elevations. Many have closed.
